               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>Oslo.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Fortum Oslo Varme AS shall enter into a framework agreement for the calibration of pressure transmitters/temperature sensors and automation services. The intention of the contract is to relieve Fortum Oslo Varme´s electrical-automation department during peak periods throughout the year.</P>
                  <P>The procurement is planned to be carried out in mid 2018, with announcement of the competition before Summer 2018. This is a prior information notice, only, and a complete tender notice with tender documents will be published at a later date. A decision has not yet been made on any possible division of the contract into sub areas /contracts.</P>
                  <P>The tenderer´s personnel ought to be able, upon bookings, to carry out calibration, upgrades, troubleshooting and instrument programming on the following process industry installation units /parametres:</P>
                  <P>— level,</P>
                  <P>— MNS-board ABB,</P>
                  <P>— pressure,</P>
                  <P>— temperature,</P>
                  <P>— amount,</P>
                  <P>— conductance,</P>
                  <P>— pH,</P>
                  <P>— environment monitoring /emissions,</P>
                  <P>— valves, engines, frequency transformers, etc.</P>
                  <P>— pumps,</P>
                  <P>— bus principles such as Foundation Fieldbus, profibus, modbus, ethernet, controlnet, devicenet, etc.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <INFO_ADD>
                  <P>Individual dialogue meetings will be held for this procurement with tenderers in week 16. For further information, any registration and requests for meeting documents, contact August Schirmer on email: august.schirmer@partners.fortum.com or tel: 47 40 97 09.</P>
                  <P>The deadline for registering is 13.4.2018 by 12:00.</P>
               </INFO_ADD>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
            <DATE_PUBLICATION_NOTICE>2018-05-21</DATE_PUBLICATION_NOTICE>
